<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>SwiftTrack Global Courier</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-inner">
    <div>SwiftTrack Global Courier — Sandton, Johannesburg</div>
    <div class="topbar-links">
      <a href="#">Customer Service</a>
      <a href="#">ZA: +27 11 000 0000</a>
      <a href="#">Login</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M1 3h15v13H1V3zm15 5h4l3 3v5h-7V8zM6 19a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4zm13 0a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="logo-text">
        SwiftTrack
        <span>Global Courier</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#" class="active">Track</a>
      <a href="#">Services</a>
      <a href="#">Routes</a>
      <a href="#">About</a>
      <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <h1>Express <span>Worldwide</span> Delivery</h1>
      <p>From Sandton to Seoul and everywhere between — SwiftTrack moves your documents across 220 countries with speed, precision, and complete visibility.</p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">220+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Countries</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">2 Days</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Korea Transit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-num">99.6%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">On-Time Rate</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="track-card">
      <h2>Track a Parcel</h2>
      <div class="track-input-row">
        <input type="text" id="trackingInput" placeholder="Enter your tracking number" maxlength="20" oninput="this.value = this.value.toUpperCase()">
        <button class="track-btn" onclick="trackParcel()">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"/></svg>
          Track
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-codes">
        Example format: <span style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:#3D3D3D;">SWT-00000-ZA</span> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <span style="font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:#3D3D3D;">SWT-00000-KR</span>
      </div>
      <div id="result"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services">
  <div class="services-inner">
    <div class="section-label">What We Offer</div>
    <div class="section-title">Our Services</div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-title">Document Delivery</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Secure, express delivery of academic and legal documents to universities and institutions worldwide.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-title">Economy Shipping</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Reliable and cost-effective delivery for non-urgent parcels worldwide.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-title">Freight Solutions</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Heavy cargo and bulk freight handled with specialist equipment and routing.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-title">Secure Parcels</div>
        <div class="service-desc">High-value items shipped with enhanced security, insurance, and chain of custody.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="service-title">International Routes</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Direct connections to South Korea, Asia-Pacific, Europe, and the Americas.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="route-highlight">
  <div class="route-highlight-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label">Featured Corridor</div>
      <div class="section-title">South Africa → South Korea</div>
      <p>Departing from our Sandton headquarters, documents reach South Korean universities in just 2 days via air freight — with two optimised routing options, full live tracking, and guaranteed delivery windows for time-sensitive admissions submissions.</p>
      <div>
        <div class="route-tag">● SDT → DXB → ICN (Seoul)</div>
        <div class="route-tag">● SDT → SIN → ICN (Seoul)</div>
        <div class="route-tag">● SDT → DXB → Jeonju</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="route-map">
      <div class="route-map-title">Active University Destinations</div>
      <div class="route-path">
        <div class="route-node">
          <div class="node-circle">A</div>
          <div class="node-info">
            <div class="node-city">Hankuk University of Foreign Studies</div>
            <div class="node-role">Office of International Admissions — Seoul 02450</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="node-arrow" style="padding-left:0; margin: 8px 0;">·</div>
        <div class="route-node">
          <div class="node-circle">B</div>
          <div class="node-info">
            <div class="node-city">Jeonbuk National University (JBNU)</div>
            <div class="node-role">Office of International Affairs — Jeonju-si 54896</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-top">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div class="logo-text">SwiftTrack<span>Global Courier</span></div>
        <p>Based in Sandton, Johannesburg — connecting South Africa to the world since 2009. Fast, reliable, and fully tracked from door to door.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Services</h4>
        <a href="#">Document Delivery</a>
        <a href="#">Economy Shipping</a>
        <a href="#">Freight</a>
        <a href="#">Customs Clearance</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Company</h4>
        <a href="#">About Us</a>
        <a href="#">Careers</a>
        <a href="#">Press</a>
        <a href="#">Partners</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Support</h4>
        <a href="#">Track a Parcel</a>
        <a href="#">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#">Claims</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <div>© 2026 SwiftTrack Global Courier. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div class="footer-badges">
        <div class="badge">ISO 9001</div>
        <div class="badge">IATA Certified</div>
        <div class="badge">Korea Route Enabled</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
